<div id="event" class="editable"><h1>Planning an Event?</h1>

<h2>In Home Dining Events</h2>

<p>When planning your event, there are many details to consider. We are here to
ease your planning worries by organizing and coordinating all the details for
your event, so that you can concentrate on making the event successful and
memorable.</p>

<h2>Types of Events</h2>

<p>Whether you are planning a lunch meeting, retirement party, small
get-together or a simple dinner with friends, I have a menu to meet your
needs!</p>

